research/history/round_summaries/round_0198.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 保持 `expert_topk`。最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`，其中 `{b_{e,i}}` 是各 expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量静态 expert 子库，再在所选子库内做 local top-k 查表与有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“子库选择 + 查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为 `直接兼容`。当前 incumbent r196 的 objective 由 cost=0.20x 与 exceed=0.1845 近乎对半构成，但最近两次更复杂结构对照并没有买到足够便宜的 exceed 改善：r197 `lowrank_expert_topk` 用 +0.03 cost 只换回 -0.0079 exceed，r191 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 也只是 +0.03 cost 换 -0.0086 exceed，说明当前前沿更像 cost 受限而不是继续加 trunk/shared 分支就会赢。相对 r196 仅把 `K` 从 96 降到 80，保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变；，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。只要 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 的上升小于 0.0156，这轮 objective 就会优于 r196；这正好回答当前更关键的问题：在 active-path 已扩到 2 experts 之后，当前最佳兼容 family 是否还存在可兑现的 small-K slack。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0198.json:36:      "最近的结构扩展 `lowrank_expert_topk` 与 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 都只拿到约 0.008 的 exceed 改善，却各自多付约 0.03 total_cost_ratio，说明在当前 0.20x-0.25x 带里，额外 trunk/shared 路径还没有证明自己值回票价。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0221.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `lowrank_factorized_residual`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S(h(x-r(x)))} \u03b1_i(x) b_i`\uff0c\u53ef\u7b49\u4ef7\u7406\u89e3\u4e3a `x_hat = trunk(x) + sparse_residual(x)`\uff1b\u5176\u4e2d `{u_r}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{b_i}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`h(\u00b7)` \u662f factorized residual scorer \u7684\u4e2d\u95f4\u8868\u793a\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201clow-rank trunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + factorized residual \u9009\u62e9 + residual \u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u662f\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar217\u3001r218\u3001r219\u3001r220 \u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u5426\u5b9a factorized-shared\u3001shared-lowrank\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca factorized selector \u8fd9\u4e9b\u201c\u76f4\u63a5\u6539\u9009\u62e9\u94fe\u8def\u201d\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\uff0c\u4f46\u5f53\u524d remaining compatible families \u91cc\uff0c`lowrank_factorized_residual` \u4ecd\u662f\u5c11\u6570 exact total_cost \u7ef4\u6301\u5728 `~0.19x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u3001\u4e14\u5c1a\u672a\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u505a\u8fc7 matched probe \u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_factorized_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4ee5\u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201c\u66f4\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 low-rank trunk + factorized residual path\uff0c\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u4e0d\u663e\u8457\u62ac\u9ad8\u603b\u6210\u672c\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a exceed \u538b\u56de\u53ef\u8d62\u533a\u95f4\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=557056\u3001deployment_accesses=245760\u3001combined_accesses=802816\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u589e\u52a0\u4e86 0.02734375\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d anchor\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.1641312575`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4f9d\u7136\u504f\u9ad8\uff0c\u4f46\u6bd4\u6700\u8fd1\u51e0\u8f6e `0.2148x` \u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u8981\u6c42\u7684 `\u22640.1407` \u73b0\u5b9e\u5f97\u591a\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u5b83\u6d4b\u8bd5\u7684\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4ecd\u672a\u88ab\u76f4\u63a5\u88c1\u51b3\u7684\u201c\u4f4e\u79e9 trunk + \u8f7b\u91cf residual scorer\u201d\u65b9\u5411\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0221.json:36:      "r218 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e0e r219 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` \u5206\u522b\u5f97\u5230 objective=0.437249 / 0.435236\uff0c\u4e14 exceed \u90fd\u5728 `0.220+`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e shared-lowrank expert \u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u7684 matched recipe \u4e0b\u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0224.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `lowrank_grouped_residual`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_G(x-trunk(x))} \u03b1_i(x) b_i`\uff0c\u5373 `x_hat = trunk(x) + sparse_residual(x)`\uff1b\u5176\u4e2d `{u_r}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{b_i}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`S_G(\u00b7)` \u8868\u793a grouped residual selector \u7ed9\u51fa\u7684\u652f\u6301\u96c6\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201clow-rank trunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + grouped residual \u9009\u62e9 + residual \u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u662f\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar222 \u4e0e r223 \u5df2\u7ecf\u8bf4\u660e plain residual \u4e0e JumpReLU residual \u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u51e0\u4e4e\u7ed9\u51fa\u76f8\u540c\u7684\u5931\u8d25\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u4f46\u5b83\u4eec\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\u56de\u7b54\u201c\u66f4\u7ed3\u6784\u5316\u7684 grouped support \u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u201d\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u4e0d\u6539\u53d8\u6210\u672c\u91cf\u7ea7\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u663e\u8457\u6539\u5584 tail error\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_grouped_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4ee5\u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5 grouped support \u662f\u5426\u6bd4 plain / JumpReLU residual \u66f4\u9002\u5408\u5f53\u524d hookpoint\u3002\u672c\u5730\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1081344\u3001deployment_accesses=245760\u3001combined_accesses=1327104\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.31640625\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u589e\u52a0\u4e86 0.15234375\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d anchor\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.0391312575`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4f9d\u7136\u6781\u5176\u6fc0\u8fdb\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u672c\u8f6e\u4ecd\u662f\u7ed3\u6784\u88c1\u51b3\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u73b0\u5b9e\u593a\u51a0\u70b9\uff1a\u5982\u679c grouped support \u5728\u4e0e r222/r223 \u76f8\u540c\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u4ecd\u4e0d\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u538b\u4f4e exceed\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u6574\u4e2a lowrank residual-support \u7ebf\u90fd\u53ef\u4ee5\u4e00\u5e76\u964d\u7ea7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0186.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `lowrank_factorized_residual`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S(h(r(x)))} α_i(h(r(x))) b_i`，其中 `r(x)=x-Σ_r β_r(x) u_r`，`h(r)=ReLU(B r)`；`{u_r}` 是静态 low-rank trunk library，`{b_i}` 是静态 residual library。在线侧可直接导出为 “trunk 系数计算 + trunk 查表加权和 -> residual 形成 -> factorized scorer 选 K 个静态 residual 原子 -> residual 查表加权和” 的 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，最终仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属 `不兼容`，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 low-cost 主问题已经从 ‘同 family 再补 K/LATENTS 插值’ 转向 ‘谁能在更小 K 下让 FVU 降得更慢’；相对 r181 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `topk` 切到 `lowrank_factorized_residual`，保持 `K=96, EF=1, TRUNK_RANK=16, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 与其余训练配方不变，可以最干净地测试：让便宜的 low-rank trunk 先吃掉平滑主干、再把小 `K` 留给 factorized residual sparse support，是否能在 `<0.25x` 主战场内明显优于 `topk@K96`，并逼近当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本 anchors。已做，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0186.json:42:      "如果该点仍明显弱于 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors，且只比 `topk@K96` 小幅改善或无改善，则可更明确下调当前 factorized residual 低成本方向的优先级，转向新的非 factorized small-`K` 槽位。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0149.json:20:    "summary": "建议以 r148 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`。这是一次面向 0.20x 低成本带的结构复验，目标不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk`，而是直接回答“expert 内 low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert recipe 下是否能形成比现有低成本锚点更有价值的新段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0149.json:43:      "若该点仍明显劣于同成本 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 锚点，则可更明确地下调 `factorized_expert_topk` 以及相关 expert-internal low-rank 无 shared/residual 线的优先级。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0149.json:64:    "description": "建议以 r148 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`。这是一次面向 0.20x 低成本带的结构复验，目标不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk`，而是直接回答“expert 内 low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert recipe 下是否能形成比现有低成本锚点更有价值的新段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0126.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0126.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库与 routed expert 子库都是真正静态向量库，在线导出仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”链路，因此 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是不兼容，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r124-r125 已经在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的压缩线上连续两轮没有形成新前沿，按规则应切 family 或切结构假设；而当前提示里仍明确指出，对 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 更有信息量的方向是“更窄 per-expert width + 更多 active routed experts”的 matched-cost 扫描。相对 r117 仅把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 192 降到 160，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_expert_topk`、`K=64`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3`、`EF=1`、`adam`、`8e-4` 不变，直接测试 active routed experts 增到 3 之后，是否可以用更窄 expert 宽度把总成本左移，同时保住或接近 r117 的质量。按已有成本轨迹估算，这会把 r117 约 0.27x 的总成本进一步压向约 0.23x-0.24x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束；如果 FVU 仍能维持在约 0.144 或更低，则这条“窄宽度 + 多 routed experts”子线有机会在当前最欠覆盖的低成本带形成新的 Pareto 锚点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0126.json:20:    "summary": "停止继续沿 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的压缩线做第三个近邻点，切回高优先级 MoE-like 方向。以 r117 为 reference，只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 192 降到 160，测试 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3` 下能否用更窄 expert 宽度换取更低总成本，并形成新的低成本结构段。",
