research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 保持为 `lowrank_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`：其中 `{u_r}` 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，`{b_{e,i}}` 是静态 expert 子库原子；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数与轻量 router，再在少量静态 expert 子库内做局部 top-k，最终仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能保留历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 `<0.25x` 主战场里，最近的 architecture-level probes `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`、`factorized_topk` 已在 matched low-cost recipe 下给出明确负信号，而 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` / `factorized_expert_topk` 也已有更早低成本负信号；相对之下，`lowrank_expert_topk` 仍是唯一在当前 low-cost 带内离现有 anchor 最近、且尚未完成 trunk 压缩定界的兼容 family。相对 r170 只把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 `16` 降到 `8`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`、`K=96`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“低秩 trunk 是否还能进一步左移到约 0.23x，同时保住足够接近当前 0.23x-0.24x anchors 的质量”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r170 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。虽然当前策略偏好 architecture-level probe，但最近两轮已经用 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 与 `factorized_topk` 补过新的低成本结构证据，且结果都偏负；继续切向已知低成本负信号更强的 family，信息增量反而更低。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk@TRUNK_RANK=8`，是因为它仍是当前 `<0.25x` 带内最接近现有 anchors 的非主线兼容 family，而 trunk 压缩是尚未完成的高信息量结构轴。主要风险是 rank=8 过薄导致 FVU 明显回退；但若不做这一步，就无法判断这条 family 是否还能在更左的 0.23x 附近保住竞争力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:36:      "最近 low-cost architecture probes 已给出更清晰负信号：r172/r174 的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍明显弱于同带 anchors，r173 的 `factorized_topk` 更显著落后；当前不应再让这些 family 主导 `<0.25x` 预算。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r170 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。虽然当前策略偏好 architecture-level probe，但最近两轮已经用 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 与 `factorized_topk` 补过新的低成本结构证据，且结果都偏负；继续切向已知低成本负信号更强的 family，信息增量反而更低。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk@TRUNK_RANK=8`，是因为它仍是当前 `<0.25x` 带内最接近现有 anchors 的非主线兼容 family，而 trunk 压缩是尚未完成的高信息量结构轴。主要风险是 rank=8 过薄导致 FVU 明显回退；但若不做这一步，就无法判断这条 family 是否还能在更左的 0.23x 附近保住竞争力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0232.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(h(x))} \u03b1_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(h(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + \u03a3_m \u03b3_m(r(x)) c_m`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `h(x)=Bx` \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4 bottleneck\uff0c`U={u_i}` \u662f shared low-rank \u9759\u6001\u5e93\uff0c`{B_e}` \u662f routed expert \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c`C={c_m}` \u662f residual \u9759\u6001\u8865\u507f\u5e93\uff0c`r(x)` \u662f shared+routed \u91cd\u6784\u540e\u7684\u6b8b\u5dee\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared low-rank \u6295\u5f71 + shared/routed \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + residual cleanup \u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u5c5e\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1aRound 229 \u4e0e Round 230 \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e residual cleanup \u786e\u5b9e\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u964d\u4f4e exceed\uff0c\u800c Round 231 \u53c8\u8bc1\u660e factorized shared+routed residual \u8fc7\u8f7b\uff0c\u5b88\u4e0d\u4f4f\u8fd9\u90e8\u5206\u6536\u76ca\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u95ee\u9898\u662f\uff0c\u66f4\u5f3a\u4f46\u4ecd\u4f4e\u7ef4\u7684 shared low-rank \u8def\u5f84\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u4fdd\u4f4f cleanup \u6536\u76ca\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u88c1\u51b3\u201cshared low-rank trunk + routed residual experts\u201d\u8fd9\u6761\u66f4\u5f3a shared \u8def\u5f84\u672c\u8eab\u503c\u4e0d\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1785856\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=1949696\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.46484375\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 r212 \u7684 objective=0.35553750753402713\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed_alpha_0.50 \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u2264-0.10930624246597288`\uff0c\u8fd9\u5728\u6570\u5b66\u4e0a\u5df2\u4e0d\u73b0\u5b9e\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u8fd1\u7aef\u7ffb\u76d8\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u7ed3\u6784\u88c1\u51b3\uff1a\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u4ecd\u65e0\u6cd5\u628a exceed \u660e\u663e\u538b\u5230\u4f18\u4e8e r229/r230 \u7684\u6863\u4f4d\uff0c\u5219 shared-lowrank residual \u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u4e5f\u5e94\u6574\u4f53\u964d\u7ea7\u3002",
